>Welcome to the Mzadat Help Center! Whether youre a seasoned bidder or a first-time user, this page is designed to provide you with the information you need to navigate our platform effectively. If you have any questions or concerns that are not addressed here.<\\/span><br \\/><\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><u>Getting Started<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Creating an Account:<\\/b><\\/p><p>To start bidding on exciting items, you need to create an account. Check our guide on how to set up your account securely and efficiently.<\\/p><p><b>2. Navigating the Dashboard:<\\/b><br \\/><\\/p><p>Learn how to explore auctions, view item details, and manage your bids through our intuitive user dashboard.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><u>Placing Bids<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. How to Place a Bid:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Step-by-step instructions on placing bids to ensure youre in the running for your desired items.<\\/p><p><b>2. Automatic Bidding (Proxy Bidding):<\\/b><br \\/><\\/p><p>Understand how our automatic bidding system works to help you stay ahead in auctions.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><u>Managing Your Account<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Updating Account Information:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Learn how to keep your account details up-to-date, including changing your password and updating payment information.<\\/p><p><b>2. Notifications and Alerts:<\\/b><br \\/><\\/p><p>Customize your notification preferences to stay informed about auction updates, bid status, and more.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><u>Selling Items<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Listing Items for Auction:<\\/b><\\/p><p>If youre looking to sell, check our guide on creating compelling listings and attracting potential buyers.<\\/p><p><b>2. Managing Your Listings:<\\/b><br \\/><\\/p><p>Learn how to edit, renew, or end your auctions, and track the performance of your listed items.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><u>Payments and Fees<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Understanding Fees:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Get an overview of our fee structure, including listing fees, final value fees, and other applicable charges.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size:1rem;\\\"><b>2. Making Payments:<\\/b><\\/span><br \\/><\\/p><p>Guidance on making secure and seamless payments for your won items.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\"><u>Troubleshooting and FAQs<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Common Issues:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Find solutions to common problems users encounter during auctions and bidding.<\\/p><p><b>2. Frequently Asked Questions:<\\/b><br \\/><\\/p><p>Explore our comprehensive FAQs for quick answers to the most commonly asked questions.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><u><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\">Policies and Guidelines<\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Terms and Conditions:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Review our terms and conditions to understand the rules governing the use of our platform.<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size:1rem;\\\"><b>2. Privacy Policy:<\\/b><\\/span><br \\/><\\/p><p>Learn about how we handle your personal information and ensure your privacy.<\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18px;\\\">Contact Us<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p>Still Need Help?<\\/p><p>If you cant find the information youre looking for, or if you have specific concerns, feel free to reach out to our support team at <b>info@mzadat.om .<\\/b><\\/p><p><br \\/><\\/p><p>Thank you for choosing <b>Mzadat<\\/b><\\/p><p><b><br \\/><\\/b>! Happy bidding!<\\/p>\"}',2,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2025-05-28 12:57:27'),(18,7,'faq','b36430a','{\"main_title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"faqs\":{\"1\":{\"title\":\"How can I place a bid on an item?\",\"description\":\"Bidding is easy! Simply navigate to the item youreinterested in, enter your bid amount, and click the \\\"Place Bid\\\" button. Make sure to review your bid before confirming. Youll receive real-time updates on the bidding status of the item.\"},\"2\":{\"title\":\"What payment methods are accepted?\",\"description\":\"We accept various secure payment methods, including major credit cards and digital payment options. Payment details will be provided at the end of a successful auction. Rest assured, all transactions are encrypted for your security.\"},\"3\":{\"title\":\"Can I track the status of my bids?\",\"description\":\"Yes, you can track your bids in real-time. Visit the \\\"My Bids\\\" section in your account to view the items youve bid on, their current status, and whether you are the highest bidder.\"},\"4\":{\"title\":\"How can I ensure the authenticity of items?\",\"description\":\"We prioritize transparency and authenticity. Each item is accompanied by detailed descriptions and, when available, provenance information. Our team thoroughly vets items to ensure their legitimacy and quality.\"},\"5\":{\"title\":\"Is my personal information secure?\",\"description\":\"Yes, we take the security of your information seriously. Our website employs encryption protocols to safeguard your personal and payment details. Refer to our Privacy Policy for more details on data protection measures.\"}}}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(19,8,'all-product','a7f9e10','{\"display_per_page\":\"9\",\"storted_by\":\"desc\",\"product_type\":\"auction\",\"sidebar_enable\":\"no\"}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(20,9,'all-product','446218b','{\"display_per_page\":\"9\",\"storted_by\":\"desc\",\"product_type\":\"direct\",\"sidebar_enable\":\"no\"}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(21,10,'all-product','6c8a840','{\"display_per_page\":null,\"storted_by\":\"desc\",\"product_type\":\"all\",\"sidebar_enable\":\"yes\"}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(22,11,'all-store','aa0deb4','{\"display_per_page\":\"9\",\"order_by_blogs\":\"asc\"}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(23,12,'procedures','e89d8be','{\"procedures\":{\"1\":{\"name\":\"Register Now & Start Selleing Your Things\",\"img\":\"egens-AQ4uTeHjEa.png\",\"button_text\":\"Register Account\",\"button_url\":\"#\",\"description\":\"Users need to create an account on the auction website. This usually involves providing personal information, creating a username, and setting a password. Some auction websites may require users to verify their email address or mobile number to activate their accounts.\\r\\n\\r\\nUsers can browse through a variety of product listings on the auction website. These listings may include images, detailed descriptions, and starting bid prices.\"},\"2\":{\"name\":\"Select Your Item\",\"img\":\"egens-HF2SWEktqW.png\",\"button_text\":\"Add Your Item\",\"button_url\":\"#\",\"description\":\"Interested buyers can participate in auctions by placing bids on items they wish to purchase. Each bid increases the current bid amount, and the auction continues until a specified end time. Users can monitor the progress of auctions theyre interested in. Notifications or alerts may be provided to inform users if they are outbid.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe user with the highest bid at the end of the auction wins the item. Some auction websites may employ automatic bidding systems where users can set a maximum bid, and the system automatically places bids on their behalf until the maximum is reached.\"},\"3\":{\"name\":\"Purcahse Items\",\"img\":\"egens-dmUZhCh2mE.png\",\"button_text\":\"Purchase Item\",\"button_url\":\"#\",\"description\":\"After winning an auction, the buyer needs to proceed with payment. The auction website typically provides multiple payment options, such as credit\\/debit cards, online payment platforms, or other forms of electronic payment. Buyers are required to provide shipping details, including the shipping address. Some auction websites may offer integrated shipping services or partnerships with logistics companies.\\r\\n\\r\\nOnce payment is confirmed, the seller ships the item to the buyer. Buyers receive the purchased item and can confirm the receipt on the auction website.\"}}}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(24,13,'all-product','446218b','{\"display_per_page\":\"9\",\"storted_by\":\"desc\",\"product_type\":\"direct\",\"sidebar_enable\":\"no\"}',1,1,'2024-01-21 19:05:00','2024-01-21 19:05:00'),(25,7,'about-content','74c7103',NULL,2,1,'2025-06-13 14:36:15','2025-06-13 14:36:15'),(28,5,'code-editor','db02f39','{\"content\":\"<p align=\\\"center\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;text-align:center;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><u><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Terms and\\nConditions<\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><u><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><b><u><\\/u><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">1.\\nDefinitions:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Website\\/Platform:\\nrefers to the electronic platform of Mazadat Company through which auctions are\\ndisplayed and managed.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Customer:\\nthe person or entity offering products or assets for sale via electronic\\nauction.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Bidder:\\nthe person or company bidding on and purchasing products through the platform.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Auction:\\nthe process by which a product is offered for bidding between multiple parties,\\nwith the highest bidder winning.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">2.\\nRegistration and Use of the Platform:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">All\\nusers must register using correct and complete information, including full\\nname, ID\\/commercial registration number, mobile number, and email address.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The\\nbidder acknowledges that all information provided is correct and up-to-date,\\nand bears full responsibility for any false or misleading information.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The\\nbidder is obligated to maintain the confidentiality of their login information\\n(username and password) and is responsible for all activities that occur under\\ntheir account.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Mazadat\\nCompany reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts that provide false\\ninformation or violate the terms and conditions.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The company is committed to protecting bidder\\ndata and not sharing it with any third party without permission.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">3.\\nBidding System:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Bidding begins at the starting price specified\\nby the customer and the auction company.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Bidding is conducted electronically and\\ntransparently, and all bids are automatically recorded on the platform.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Two minutes will be added if bidding occurs\\nwithin the last two minutes, and this process continues until bidders stop\\nbidding.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The specified deposit amount for each auction\\nmust be paid to participate in the auction.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The sale will not be approved until the\\ncustomer approves the sale.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">4.\\nGuarantees and Financial Obligations:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Deposit Amount: Each bidder is required to pay\\na deposit before entering the auction. This amount is used to ensure\\nseriousness in purchasing and compliance with the terms.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">If the winning bidder fails to pay the final\\namount within the specified period (three business days from the invoice date),\\nthe transaction will be canceled and the full deposit amount will be forfeited.\\nThis action is considered compensation for any resulting damages.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The security deposit will not be refunded if\\nthe loading site (yard) is not cleaned or waste is left after receiving the\\nmaterials.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">A daily fee of OMR 20 per day will be deducted\\nfrom the security deposit if the winning bidder delays transporting the\\nmaterials after the specified period.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">No product will be delivered until payment is\\nconfirmed.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The buyer bears the shipping or receiving\\ncosts, if any.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">5.\\nFees and Commissions:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The company charges a specific administrative\\nfee for each auction, deducted from the final auction price.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The brokerage fee is collected from the buyer\\naccording to the specified and agreed-upon percentage.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Taxes or customs duties may be imposed on the\\nitems to be sold.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">6.\\nWarranty and Liability<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Auctions Company and customers are not directly\\nresponsible for the condition or quality of the products unless expressly\\nstated, and the buyer must carefully inspect the items before registering for\\nthe auction.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">-<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Items are sold in their current location and\\ncondition as is.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Auctions\\nCompany and customers are not responsible for any fees that may be imposed on\\nitems.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">7.\\nVehicle Ownership Transfer (if applicable):<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">If the\\nauction includes vehicles, the winning bidder must complete the ownership\\ntransfer procedures within a maximum of (15) business days from the date of\\nreceipt of the vehicle.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The winning bidder must pay all government fees\\ndue for the transfer of ownership, and the website will provide the required\\npaperwork and documents.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The\\nAuctions Company assumes no responsibility for the vehicle after delivery,\\nincluding its technical or legal condition, and the winning bidder accepts its\\ncondition as is.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The\\nbuyer may be required to sign additional documents to document the sale and\\ntransfer of ownership.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">8.\\nAuctions Company Powers:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The Auctions Company reserves the right to\\ncancel or extend any online auction at any time, whether due to technical or\\norganizational circumstances, or at the request of the owner of the items being\\noffered.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-left:0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\n<\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The company has the right to reopen the auction\\nor re-post the item at a later time if it deems the auction conditions\\nunsuitable or violations that affect its fairness occur.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">9.\\nCustomer Powers:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">The\\ncustomer has the right to reject the auction result if the bids do not reach\\nthe minimum price (secret minimum) previously set by the customer, provided\\nthis occurs before the final sale is completed.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">This\\nminimum must be determined in advance when the items are delivered to the\\nauction company, and the company is obligated not to approve the sale if the\\nrequired price is not reached.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0in;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">10.\\nDispute Resolution:<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <\\/span><\\/span><span dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\\\">In the\\nevent of any dispute between bidders, or between the bidder and the management,\\nit will first be resolved through direct negotiation.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin:0in 0in 5pt 0.5in;text-indent:-0.25in;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:\'Viner Hand ITC\';\\\">\\u2013<span style=\\\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 <